### Get Placeholders from Template
GET http://localhost:8080/api/pptx/placeholders?templatePath=templates/report-template.pptx
Accept: application/json

###

### Generate Presentation with Text Replacement
POST http://localhost:8080/api/pptx/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "templateName": "templates/report-template.pptx",
  "placeholders": [
    {
      "key": "companyName",
      "type": "TEXT",
      "value": "Acme Corporation"
    },
    {
      "key": "reportTitle",
      "type": "TEXT",
      "value": "Q4 2024 Financial Report"
    },
    {
      "key": "date",
      "type": "TEXT",
      "value": "December 31, 2024"
    },
    {
      "key": "revenue",
      "type": "TEXT",
      "value": "$1,250,000"
    }
  ]
}

###

### Generate Presentation with Text and Image
POST http://localhost:8080/api/pptx/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "templateName": "templates/report-template.pptx",
  "placeholders": [
    {
      "key": "title",
      "type": "TEXT",
      "value": "Annual Report 2024"
    },
    {
      "key": "logo",
      "type": "IMAGE",
      "value": {
        "imageBytes": "iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVR42mNk+M9QDwADhgGAWjR9awAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==",
        "contentType": "image/png",
        "pictureType": 6
      }
    }
  ]
}

###

### Modify Presentation (Returns Bytes)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/pptx/modify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "templateName": "templates/simple-template.pptx",
  "placeholders": [
    {
      "key": "greeting",
      "type": "TEXT",
      "value": "Hello World"
    }
  ]
}

###

### Generate with INSERT (Partial Replacement)
# Template: "Цена: $цена руб." → "Цена: 1000 руб."
POST http://localhost:8080/api/pptx/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "templateName": "templates/invoice-template.pptx",
  "placeholders": [
    {
      "key": "цена",
      "type": "INSERT",
      "value": "1000"
    },
    {
      "key": "количество",
      "type": "INSERT",
      "value": "5"
    },
    {
      "key": "дата",
      "type": "INSERT",
      "value": "03.12.2024"
    }
  ]
}

